name: Madrugada
description:
This song is very special for me and I like it a lot because it was the first time I collaborated with a producer (J.V.O) and the experience was super good. The process with J.V.O was very easy and everything flowed smoothly since he is an experienced producer and has been producing rhythms and performing at important festivals for a long time. This song was released on June 16, 2021 and is now available as #MusicNFT to be preserved for all time.

Artist- Sad Blu 
Producer- JVO, Sad Blu 
Cover Art- Sad Blu
